# JSDoc (minimal)

**Scope:** doc comments on functions, methods, exported arrow fns in matched files.

**Block (directly above symbol):** `@brief` (one line: behavior) · `@param {Type} name - …` (every arg) · `@returns {Type} …` or `{void}` (`@return` OK).

**Shapes:** `@typedef` / `@property` → each `@property {Type} name - …`.
